## ğŸ›  How to Design the Bot for Safety

| Feature                     | Description                                                                                   |
| --------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **No prescription logic**   | Never recommend dosage or medicine                                                            |
| **Conditional responses**   | Use phrases like â€œmay beâ€, â€œpossibleâ€, â€œsuggest seeing a doctorâ€                              |
